grades.title: HP1
grades.summary: MVR (300°C/1.2kg) 25, biocompatible, sterilizable PC, medical devices
grades.description: LEXAN HP1 is a high flow polycarbonate (PC) with an MVR (300°C/1.2kg) of 25. This is a biocompatible (ISO10993 or USP Class VI) grade for medical devices and pharmaceutical applications. It is EtO and steam sterilizable, contains mold release and adheres to our healthcare management of change policy.
